    },
    {
      "Text": "An update for jbig2dec is now available for openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP4",
      "Title": "Summary",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "jbig2dec is a decoder implementation of the JBIG2 image compression format.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nAn integer overflow in the jbig2_arith_iaid_ctx_new() function of Artifex commit cc37d0 allows attackers to cause a Denial of Service (DoS) via a crafted input.(CVE-2026-38076)",
      "Title": "Description",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "An update for jbig2dec is now available for openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP4.\n\nopenEuler Security has rated this update as having a security impact of high. A Common Vunlnerability Scoring System(CVSS)base score,which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVElink(s) in the References section.",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "High",
      "Title": "Severity",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "jbig2dec",
      "Title": "Affected Component",
      "Type": "General"
    }
